safeClose(address,uint256,address).details: Burn Prime and Prime Redeem tokens to withdraw tokenU.

params.amount: Quantity of Prime options to mint and tokenU to deposit.
params.receiver: The newly minted tokens are sent to the receiver address.
params.tokenP: The address of the Prime Option to trade with.

safeRedeem(address,uint256,address).details: Burns Prime Redeem tokens to withdraw available tokenS.

params.amount: Quantity of Prime Redeem to spend.

safeSwap(address,uint256,address).details: Swaps tokenS to tokenU using ratio as the exchange rate.

params.amount: Quantity of Primes to use to swap.

safeUnwind(address,uint256,address).details: Burn Prime Redeem tokens to withdraw tokenU and tokenS from expired options.

safeClose(address,uint256,address).notice: Takes paramter for quantity of Primes to burn. The Prime Redeems to burn is equal to the Primes * ratio.

safeMint(address,uint256,address).notice: Also mints Prime Redeem tokens. Calls msg.sender with transferFrom.

safeSwap(address,uint256,address).notice: Burns Prime, contract receives tokenS, user receives tokenU. Calls msg.sender with transferFrom.

safeUnwind(address,uint256,address).notice: Takes paramter for quantity of Primes to burn. The Prime Redeems to burn is equal to the Primes * ratio.
